Ramiel and Gogolan received a call just as they were starting the 
Conference.

??????: Agents Ramiel and Gogolan, you are to meet with Exploration 
Vessel Outbound Light. You are required on planet Banipal for your 
botanics class. Any lateness will get you two in detention after 
school.

Gogolan: Uh oh... We're in deep shit...

Ramiel: Yeah... Hum... So long suckers!!!

They both run inside their ship and take off, back to outer space.

Jetstorm: I think they won't be coming back... Slag... I'm off two...

He flies back to Australia.
